The Anti-Dump Engine and Token Lifecycle Control transform token behavior from:

«“Acquire → Dump”
into
“Acquire → Use → Earn → Sustain”»

By aligning unlocks, selling power, and incentives with trust and utility:

«The system protects itself from within.»

